           C1 1_555  C2  1_555  C3 1_555 1  'Benzene ring with mirror symmetry'
           C2 1_555  C3  1_555  C4 2_655 2  ?
           C4 1_555  C5  1_555  C6 1_555 2  ?
           C5 1_555  C6  1_555  C1 1_555 1  ?
;
    _description_example.detail
