#============================================================================

    _dictionary_author.id         1
    _dictionary_author.name       'Brown, I. D.'
    _dictionary_author.id_orcid   0000-0002-6267-2692
    _dictionary_author.email      .

    loop_
      _dictionary_audit.version
      _dictionary_audit.date
      _dictionary_audit.revision

         3.1.0                    2016-11-16
;
       Initial CIF2 version created from STAR2 version provided by Syd Hall
       (J Hester)
;
         3.1.1                    2026-06-08
;
       Fixed a CIF2 syntax error.

       Removed the _description.text data item from
       the 'restr_angle.atom_site_label_1', 'restr_angle.atom_site_label_2'
       and 'restr_angle.atom_site_label_3' save frames since the same data
       item is already provided in the imported 'restr_label' save frame.

       Updated the CIF_CORE dictionary import statement with the new Head
       category name.

       (A. Vaitkus)

       2025-11-24: Changed Head category name for this dictionary and updated
       _dictionary.namespace in accordance with COMCIFS principles. (bm)

       2025-11-27: Tidied layout in accordance with dictionary style
       guidelines; removed all instances of the _category.key_id attribute
       since it is no longer defined in the DDLm reference dictionary;
       clarified the interpretation of the enumeration details in
       _restr_parameter_class.parameter_type (e.g. 'atom_site.occupancy'
       -> 'Value of _atom_site.occupancy'). (bm)

       2026-01-23: Replaced 'restr_label' imports with 'atom_site_id' imports.

       2026-01-23: Replaced all 'Measurand' values as 'Number'
       (because constraints and restraints are specified during
       refinement and not taken from the experiment) and likewise
       changed their _type.source from 'Derived' to 'Assigned'. (bm)

       2026-01-26: Added _units.code to _restr_angle.target_weight_param,
       _restr_distance_min.a, *_c and *_e (these three dimensionless),
       _restr_equal_angle_class.target_weight_param,
       _restr_parameter.atom_coefficient, _restr_parameter_class.target,
       _restr_parameter_class.target_weight_param, _restr_torsion.weight_param.

       Changed _type.purpose of _restr_rigid_body_class.class_id from
       'Encode' to 'Link'. (bm)

       2026-01-27: Changed *.average_su to *.esd in the categories
       RESTR_EQUAL_ANGLE_CLASS, RESTR_EQUAL_DISTANCE_CLASS and
       RESTR_EQUAL_TORSION_CLASS as these are true statistical e.s.d.s.
       Changed their _type.source to 'Derived' (bm).

       Revised Head category name and _dictionary.namespace as agreed in
       COMCIFS harmonisation project. (bm)

       2026-01-29: Added _enumeration.range to _restr_distance_min.F. (bm)

       Changed _type.purpose to 'Measurand' and added *_su values for
       parameters that can be refined with a standard uncertainty.

       2026-06-03: added *_su items for real *_esd definitions (because
       derived from experiment) and for _restr_U_rigid.U_parallel.

       Added category examples.

       2026-06-05: explicitly linked *.class_id data items to
       the corresponding *_class.class_id data items.

       2026-06-08: changed units of some definitions referring to
       torsion angles to degrees.

       Added explicit links to the _atom_site.label data item.
;